extendedInfo.description: It's not easy to survive in the dangerous ocean. There are many fierce fishes around you. You need to hunt fishes to grow up, and finally beat all enemies! Simple game rules:# Big fish hunts little fish.# Hunting fish to grow up. # Abundant game scenarios, volcano, ruins, glacier and more than 30 kinds of fishes. # Different ways of control to be selected - rolling, sliding and tilting by gravity accelerator.# Items will help you when you are in desperate situation.Good luck to be the fish predator!

reviews.title: Good, but could be great
reviews.comment: Enjoy the concept, but in what ocean does a great white outrank a killer whale? To make the game fantastic you need to include the largest predator of all time, the sperm whale. Also more avatars with special talents for attracting fish, or speeding up yours or making it harder to be eaten

reviews.title: Love it!
reviews.comment: Controls take some getting used to but work really well. The graphics are nice and the gameplay is fun. There is just enough material (levels, avatars, fishes, etc) to keep the game fresh and interesting. Suggestion: create new avatars that do things similar to the buyable items, or maybe have them be especially good at attracting a certain type of fish. This is my favorite game on my tablet and I can play for hours without getting bored. Thanks for making it a free game! :)
